.Dd December 22, 2003
.Dt BGPCTL 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm bgpctl
.Nd "control the Border Gateway Protocol daemon"
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm bgpctl
.Bk -words
.Ek
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
program controls the
.Xr bgpd
daemon.
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr bgpd 8
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "/etc/bgpd.conf" -compact
.It Pa /etc/bgpd.conf
.Nm
configuration file.
.El
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
program first appeared in
.Ox 3.5 .
